@page "/about/process"

@rendermode InteractiveServer

<SeoComponent Title="@pageTitle"
    Description="Learn about Ítala Veloso's transformative coaching process. Discover how our structured approach helps you overcome challenges, heal from trauma, and achieve personal breakthrough."
    Keywords="coaching process, transformation process, personal breakthrough, healing process, life coach methodology, coaching approach, self-discovery process"
    CanonicalUrl="https://italaveloso.com/about/process" JsonLdStructuredData="@GetPageStructuredData()" />

<PageTitle>@pageTitle</PageTitle>

<link href="~/css/process.css" rel="stylesheet" />
<script src="~/js/process-enhancements.js" defer></script>

<div class="process-page">
    <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1 class="process-title">The <span class="highlight">Process</span></h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">
                Discover a transformative journey that guides you from feeling stuck to truly thriving in every area of
                your life.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <main class="process-content">
        <section class="content-section" style="--delay: 0.1s;">
            <div class="section-card">
                <h2 class="section-title">
                    <div class="section-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
                    </div>
                    Are You Ready for Change?
                </h2>

                <div class="question-text">
                    Have you ever felt lost? Stuck? Not knowing what to do next with your life?
                </div>

                <p class="section-text">
                    Feeling like no matter how many therapies you tried or where you turned to before, nothing seemed to
                    work?
                    It's as if you'd reached the end of the road, shattered by circumstances or by what others did to
                    you or those you love.
                </p>

                <div class="question-text">
                    Perhaps you've recently graduated but don't know where to turn next?
                </div>

                <p class="section-text">
                    Or maybe you know what you want to do but don't want to follow conventional 9-5 patterns?
                    You'd like to start something fresh, for yourself?
                </p>

                <div class="question-text">
                    Do you find yourself stagnated, sensing you could be doing much more?
                </div>

                <p class="section-text">
                    Want to discover what's holding you back and finally let yourself grow?
                    Are you finding yourself overwhelmed and stressed lately?
                </p>

                <div class="highlight-quote">
                    Whatever your reason, if you're reading this, you might be searching for significance, change, and
                    peace in your life.
                    A shift in your mindset and decision-making process to help you close the gap between where you are
                    right now and where you'd like to be.
                </div>

                <p class="section-text">
                    <strong>You are not alone. I've been there too.</strong>
                </p>

                <p class="section-text">
                    Search no more. Let's embark on a journey of Life Coaching together, shall we?
                    Here's where everything can change: This is where you <strong>stop merely existing</strong> and
                    <strong>start truly living</strong>.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section" style="--delay: 0.2s;">
            <div class="section-card">
                <h2 class="section-title">
                    <div class="section-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-user-circle"></i>
                    </div>
                    Meet Your Guide
                </h2>

                <p class="section-text">
                    Ítala here, your Life Coach and Mentor, and founder of <span
                        class="methodology-highlight">JOSTIC</span> —
                    a lived and proven Life Liberation Methodology™. It's designed to empower and help you release your
                    true authentic self,
                    guiding you to experience a mindset shift, break the barriers of limiting beliefs, develop new
                    healthier habits,
                    and unlock paths that will lead you to continue moving forward and transform your life.
                </p>

                <p class="section-text">
                    This methodology isn't just about healing or self-discovery—it's about mastering your journey and
                    empowering every aspect of your life.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section" style="--delay: 0.3s;">
            <div class="section-card">
                <h2 class="section-title">
                    <div class="section-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-compass"></i>
                    </div>
                    Introducing JOSTIC
                </h2>

                <div class="methodology-logo">JOSTIC</div>

                <p class="section-text">
                    I retrained as a Life Coach and Mentor and developed <strong>JOSTIC</strong>, a lived and proven
                    <em>Life Liberation Methodology™</em>. It's designed to empower and give a voice to the suppressed,
                    confused,
                    and trapped emotions we all carry inside, while guiding people to break free and start thriving in
                    every area of life.
                </p>

                <div class="highlight-quote">
                    What does this mean for you? This methodology isn't just about healing or self-discovery—it's about
                    mastering your journey and empowering every aspect of your life.
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section" style="--delay: 0.4s;">
            <div class="section-card">
                <h2 class="section-title">
                    <div class="section-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                    </div>
                    What Can You Achieve?
                </h2>

                <p class="section-text">
                    Start the Most Popular 10-session Life Coaching Programme with Ítala Veloso now, and discover how
                    you can:
                </p>

                <div class="outcomes-grid">
                    <div class="outcome-card">
                        <div class="outcome-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="outcome-text">Move from feeling stuck to truly thriving</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="outcome-card">
                        <div class="outcome-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-peace"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="outcome-text">Reclaim your inner peace and reignite your passion for life</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="outcome-card">
                        <div class="outcome-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="outcome-text">Find clarity and break free from limiting beliefs and patterns</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="outcome-card">
                        <div class="outcome-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-map"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="outcome-text">Design and roadmap your future with confidence and purpose</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="outcome-card">
                        <div class="outcome-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-heart-pulse"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="outcome-text">Build healthier, stronger, more fulfilling relationships</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="outcome-card">
                        <div class="outcome-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-balance-scale"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="outcome-text">Balance work-life pressures while enhancing wellness and nurturing
                            mental health</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="outcome-card">
                        <div class="outcome-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="outcome-text">Achieve career clarity, including career path mapping, CV re-assessment,
                            and interview preparation</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="outcome-card">
                        <div class="outcome-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-target"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="outcome-text">Align your self-awareness and skills with your dreams and goals</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="section-text">
                    Whether it's your work-life, relationships, wellness, or finances—this journey is about
                    transformation.
                    It's about helping you reclaim inner peace and start living fully and freely.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section" style="--delay: 0.5s;">
            <div class="section-card">
                <h2 class="section-title">
                    <div class="section-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-route"></i>
                    </div>
                    Your Journey Steps
                </h2>

                <div class="journey-steps">
                    <div class="journey-step">
                        <div class="step-number">1</div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <h3 class="step-title">Discovery & Assessment</h3>
                            <p class="step-description">We start by understanding where you are now, what's holding you
                                back, and what you truly want to achieve.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="journey-step">
                        <div class="step-number">2</div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <h3 class="step-title">JOSTIC Framework Application</h3>
                            <p class="step-description">Using the proven Life Liberation Methodology™, we begin breaking
                                through limiting beliefs and patterns.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="journey-step">
                        <div class="step-number">3</div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <h3 class="step-title">Transformation & Growth</h3>
                            <p class="step-description">Through structured sessions, you'll develop new habits, gain
                                clarity, and experience profound mindset shifts.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="journey-step">
                        <div class="step-number">4</div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <h3 class="step-title">Integration & Mastery</h3>
                            <p class="step-description">You'll learn to integrate your new insights and skills, creating
                                lasting change and continued growth.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section" style="--delay: 0.6s;">
            <div class="section-card">
                <h2 class="section-title">
                    <div class="section-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                    </div>
                    Who is This For?
                </h2>

                <p class="section-text">
                    This isn't just for one type of person or one type of struggle. My services are available in both
                    <strong>English</strong> and <strong>Portuguese</strong>, for both <strong>Female</strong> and
                    <strong>Male</strong>,
                    making them accessible to a diverse community.
                </p>

                <p class="section-text">
                    Wherever you are on your journey, I'm here to guide you—whether you need coaching, mentoring,
                    or clarity in life and career.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cta-section">
            <div class="cta-content">
                <h2 class="cta-title">Are You Ready to Transform Your Life?</h2>
                <p class="cta-text">
                    Unleash your life—it's not over yet. No matter what it feels like right now. Mine wasn't, and
                    neither is yours.
                    This can be the beginning of your transformation. Let's uncover the best version of you that is
                    fearless, alive,
                    strong, and more powerful than you've ever imagined.
                </p>
                <div class="highlight-quote"
                    style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); border-color: white; color: white;">
                    Because You are More Than A Conqueror™
                </div>
                <a href="#contact" class="cta-button">
                    <i class="fas fa-calendar-check"></i>
                    <span>Book Your Free Discovery Call</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</div>

